_fmts=0x0%2C797x280&amp;nras=3&amp;correlator=5302438728761&amp;frm=20&amp;pv=1&amp;ga_vid=826243041.1636986097&amp;ga_sid=1636986097&amp;ga_hid=1528386135&amp;ga_fc=1&amp;u_tz=0&amp;u_his=4&amp;u_h=768&amp;u_w=1366&amp;u_ah=728&amp;u_aw=1366&amp;u_cd=24&amp;dmc=8&amp;adx=74&amp;ady=1231&amp;biw=1349&amp;bih=600&amp;scr_x=0&amp;scr_y=0&amp;eid=31063702%2C31063737%2C21067496&amp;oid=2&amp;pvsid=3305327623449071&amp;pem=178&amp;tmod=1612512547&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2F&amp;eae=0&amp;fc=1408&amp;brdim=0%2C0%2C0%2C0%2C1366%2C0%2C1366%2C728%2C1366%2C600&amp;vis=1&amp;rsz=%7C%7Cs%7C&amp;abl=NS&amp;fu=128&amp;bc=31&amp;jar=2021-11-15-14&amp;ifi=3&amp;uci=a!3&amp;btvi=2&amp;fsb=1&amp;xpc=BVbM0bF4bP&amp;p=https%3A//ghextractives.com&amp;dtd=127" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" vspace="0" hspace="0" allowtransparency="true" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="true" data-google-container-id="a!3" data-load-complete="true" data-google-query-id="COGJqsvImvQCFZIGiwodv5QFMg" style="box-sizing: inherit; width: 797px; max-width: 100%; left: 0px; position: absolute; top: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; height: 0px;"></iframe></ins></ins></ins></div><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto; font-size: 15px;">He said, “It is the cost of refining gold locally which we will gain 20% free equity share but the gold belonged to the mining companies.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto; font-size: 15px;">“In fact, we do not gain anything when the gold is refined outside and so as part of efforts to providing refinery solution, the government of Ghana entered into an agreement with the Indian Investor to build a refinery here. It also formed part of government’s policy to at least refine 30% of all gold produced in Ghana,” he added.</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 26px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto; font-size: 15px;">Gomashie stated that the Indian Investor invested an estimated amount of US$25 million in constructing the gold refinery, which is located at the Diamond House on the premises of the Precious Minerals Marketing Company in Accra.</p><div class="google-auto-placed ap_container" style="box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto; font-size: 15px; width: 796.656px; height: auto; clear: both; text-align: center;"><ins data-ad-format="auto" class="adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate" data-ad-client="ca-pub-5557424465415080" data-adsbygoogle-status="done" data-ad-status="unfilled" style="box-sizing: inherit; background: transparent; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px 4px; text-decoration-line: none; display: block; margin: auto; height: 0px;"><ins id="aswift_3_expand" tabindex="0" title="Advertisement" aria-label="Advertisement" style="box-sizing: inherit; background: transparent; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; border: none; height: 0px; width: 797px; margin: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; display: inline-table;"><ins id="aswift_3_anchor" style="box-sizing: inherit; background: transparent; padding: 0px; text-decoration-line: none; border: none; height: 0px; width: 797px; margin: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; display: block; overflow: hidden; opacity: 0;"><iframe id="aswift_3" name="aswift_3" sandbox="allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation" width="797" height="0" frameborder="0" src="https://googleads.g.doubleclick.net/pagead/ads?client=ca-pub-5557424465415080&amp;output=html&amp;h=280&amp;adk=2033516795&amp;adf=395696678&amp;pi=t.aa~a.1996313127~i.15~rp.4&amp;w=797&amp;fwrn=4&amp;fwrnh=100&amp;lmt=1636986097&amp;num_ads=1&amp;rafmt=1&amp;armr=3&amp;sem=mc&amp;pwprc=6764320120&amp;psa=0&amp;ad_type=text_image&amp;f